       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. EMPDEL2.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-DBDATA.
           05  WS-EMPNO              PIC X(6).
           05  WS-SUCCESS            PIC X.
           05  WS-SQL-CODE           PIC S9(9) COMP-4.
           05  WS-SQL-STATE          PIC X(5).
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE MYEMP END-EXEC.
       LINKAGE SECTION.
       01  DFHCOMMAREA.
            COPY DELCP.
      *
       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING DFHCOMMAREA.
      *
       000-MAIN.
           PERFORM 1000-DELETE-RECORD
           PERFORM 2000-GET-ME-OUT-OF-HERE.
      *
       1000-DELETE-RECORD.
           MOVE COMM-EMPNO TO WS-EMPNO
           EXEC SQL
               DELETE FROM IBMUSER.MY_EMP WHERE EMPNO = :WS-EMPNO
           END-EXEC
           IF SQLSTATE = '00000'
               MOVE 'Y' TO COMM-SUCCESS
           ELSE
               MOVE 'N' TO COMM-SUCCESS
               MOVE SQLCODE TO COMM-SQL-CODE
               MOVE SQLSTATE TO COMM-SQL-STATE
           END-IF.
      *
       2000-GET-ME-OUT-OF-HERE.
           EXEC CICS
              RETURN
           END-EXEC.
